# {{ProjectName}}

Minimal ASP.NET Core MVC application built with Swap.Htmx framework and Bulma CSS.

## Features

- ✅ **Zero NPM Dependencies** - Bulma & HTMX via LibMan
- ✅ **Toast Notifications** - Built-in user feedback
- ✅ **Out-of-Band Swaps** - Update multiple page sections
- ✅ **Event System** - Domain events to UI events
- ✅ **SwapController** - Automatic page/partial detection

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- .NET 9.0 or higher
- LibMan CLI (optional, can use VS Code extension)

### Run the Application

```bash
cd src
dotnet restore
libman restore
dotnet run
```

Visit `https://localhost:5001` or `http://localhost:5000`

