## Key Concepts

### SwapController

All controllers inherit from `SwapController`:

```csharp
public class HomeController : SwapController
{
    public IActionResult Index()
    {
        return SwapView(); // Auto-detects page vs partial
    }
}
```

### Toast Notifications

```csharp
Response.ShowSuccessToast("Item created!");
Response.ShowErrorToast("Something went wrong");
Response.ShowWarningToast("Please review");
Response.ShowInfoToast("FYI...");
```

### Out-of-Band Swaps

Update multiple elements in one response:

```csharp
// Main content
var main = SwapView("Success");

// Update badge in header
ViewData["OobBadge"] = $@"
    <span id=""badge"" hx-swap-oob=""innerHTML"">
        {count}
    </span>";

return main;
```

### Event Chains

Configure in `Program.cs`:

```csharp
builder.Services.AddSwapHtmx(events =>
{
    events.Chain(MyEvents.ItemCreated, 
                 UiEvents.RefreshList, 
                 UiEvents.ShowToast);
});
```

